Claude CodeClaude DesktopCursorWindsurfClineZed <p>Add to <code>.mcp.json</code> in your project root:</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "opentime": {
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "opentime-mcp",
      "env": {
        "OPENTIME_DB_PATH": "~/.opentime/agent.db",
        "OPENTIME_AGENT_ID": "my-agent"
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Add to your Claude Desktop config (<code>~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json</code> on macOS):</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "opentime": {
      "command": "opentime-mcp",
      "env": {
        "OPENTIME_DB_PATH": "~/.opentime/agent.db",
        "OPENTIME_AGENT_ID": "claude-desktop"
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Add to <code>.cursor/mcp.json</code> in your project root:</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "opentime": {
      "command": "opentime-mcp",
      "env": {
        "OPENTIME_DB_PATH": "~/.opentime/agent.db",
        "OPENTIME_AGENT_ID": "cursor"
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Add to <code>~/.codeium/windsurf/mcp_config.json</code>:</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "opentime": {
      "command": "opentime-mcp",
      "env": {
        "OPENTIME_DB_PATH": "~/.opentime/agent.db",
        "OPENTIME_AGENT_ID": "windsurf"
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>In VS Code, open Cline settings and add an MCP server:</p> <ul> <li>Command: <code>opentime-mcp</code></li> <li>Env: <code>OPENTIME_DB_PATH=~/.opentime/agent.db</code>, <code>OPENTIME_AGENT_ID=cline</code></li> </ul> <p>Add to your Zed <code>settings.json</code>:</p> <pre><code>{
  "context_servers": {
    "opentime": {
      "command": {
        "path": "opentime-mcp",
        "env": {
          "OPENTIME_DB_PATH": "~/.opentime/agent.db",
          "OPENTIME_AGENT_ID": "zed"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>
